  "title": "🔥Training Sales Advisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Mentorship Provided | No Experience Required</strong></p><p>Ready to launch a rewarding career with real growth opportunities? We’re hiring an <strong>Training Sales Advisor</strong> to join our dynamic team. New to the field? That’s okay—we offer comprehensive training and dedicated 1-on-1 mentorship to set you up for success.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Consult with individuals to identify the right training programs for their goals</p></li><li><p>Support learners through enrollment and funding options</p></li><li><p>Build strong relationships and assist with common questions throughout their journey</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li><p>✔ Structured training and personalized mentorship</p></li><li><p>✔ Supportive, goal-oriented team culture</p></li><li><p>✔ Competitive incentives and clear career advancement pathways</p></li></ul><p>If you’re looking for a role that’s meaningful, people-focused, and full of potential, this is your next step.</p><p>📩 <strong>Apply today and start building your future with us!</strong></p>",
